<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>รายงานการขาย | ITMI Shop</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;700&family=Sarabun:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            --success-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%);
            --danger-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff416c 0%, #ff4b2b 100%);
            --info-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #2193b0 0%, #6dd5ed 100%);
        }

        body { 
            font-family: 'Sarabun', 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; 
            background-color: #f0f2f5; 
            color: #334155; 
        }

        .navbar { z-index: 1050 !important; box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }

        /* Header Styling */
        .page-header {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 2rem 0;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        /* Stat Cards */
        .stat-card {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }

        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }

        .stat-icon {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .bg-icon-primary { background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1); color: #667eea; }
        .bg-icon-success { background: rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.1); color: #28a745; }
        .bg-icon-danger { background: rgba(255, 65, 108, 0.1); color: #ff416c; }
        .bg-icon-info { background: rgba(33, 147, 176, 0.1); color: #2193b0; }

        /* Filter Section */
        .filter-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .form-control-custom {
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 2px solid #f1f5f9;
            padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .form-control-custom:focus {
            border-color: #667eea;
            box-shadow: none;
            background: #fdfdfd;
        }

        /* Table Styling */
        .table-container {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .table thead th {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: none;
            color: #64748b;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            padding: 1.2rem;
        }

        .table tbody td {
            padding: 1.2rem;
            vertical-align: middle;
            border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        }

        .badge-pay {
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .btn-pill {
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-primary-gradient {
            background: var(--primary-gradient);
            color: white;
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-primary-gradient:hover {
            filter: brightness(1.1);
            color: white;
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        .product-name { font-weight: 600; color: #1e293b; }
        .member-info { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #64748b; }
        
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('../navbar.ejs') %>

    <div class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-6 text-center text-md-left">
                    <h2 class="font-weight-bold mb-1">📊 รายงานวิเคราะห์การขาย</h2>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">ข้อมูลอัปเดตแบบ Real-time ของร้าน ITMI Shop</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 text-center text-md-right mt-3 mt-md-0">
                    <a href="/sales/new" class="btn btn-primary-gradient btn-pill shadow-lg">
                        <i class="fas fa-cart-plus mr-2"></i> บันทึกขายใหม่
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="filter-card mb-5 shadow-sm">
            <form action="/sales/report" method="GET" class="row align-items-end">
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold text-muted text-uppercase mb-2 d-block">ช่วงเริ่มต้น</label>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <div class="input-group-prepend">
                            <span class="input-group-text bg-white border-right-0" style="border-radius: 12px 0 0 12px; border: 2px solid #f1f5f9;"><i class="far fa-calendar-alt"></i></span>
                        </div>
                        <input type="date" name="startDate" class="form-control form-control-custom border-left-0" value="<%= startDate %>">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold text-muted text-uppercase mb-2 d-block">สิ้นสุดวันที่</label>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <div class="input-group-prepend">
                            <span class="input-group-text bg-white border-right-0" style="border-radius: 12px 0 0 12px; border: 2px solid #f1f5f9;"><i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i></span>
                        </div>
                        <input type="date" name="endDate" class="form-control form-control-custom border-left-0" value="<%= endDate %>">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="d-flex">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark btn-pill flex-grow-1 mr-2 shadow-sm">
                            <i class="fas fa-filter mr-2"></i> กรองข้อมูล
                        </button>
                        <a href="/sales/report" class="btn btn-light btn-pill border shadow-sm" title="ล้างค่า">
                            <i class="fas fa-undo"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="row mb-5">
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card stat-card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="stat-icon bg-icon-primary"><i class="fas fa-coins"></i></div>
                        <h6 class="text-muted font-weight-bold mb-1">ยอดขายรวม</h6>
                        <h3 class="font-weight-bold mb-0 text-dark"><%= stats.totalRevenue.toLocaleString() %> <small class="h6 text-muted">฿</small></h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card stat-card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="stat-icon bg-icon-success"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i></div>
                        <h6 class="text-muted font-weight-bold mb-1">กำไรสุทธิ</h6>
                        <h3 class="font-weight-bold mb-0 text-success"><%= stats.totalProfit.toLocaleString() %> <small class="h6 text-muted font-weight-bold">฿</small></h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card stat-card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="stat-icon bg-icon-danger"><i class="fas fa-percentage"></i></div>
                        <h6 class="text-muted font-weight-bold mb-1">ส่วนลดสะสม</h6>
                        <h3 class="font-weight-bold mb-0 text-danger"><%= stats.totalDiscount.toLocaleString() %> <small class="h6 text-muted">฿</small></h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card stat-card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="stat-icon bg-icon-info"><i class="fas fa-qrcode"></i></div>
                        <h6 class="text-muted font-weight-bold mb-1">รับผ่าน QR Code</h6>
                        <h3 class="font-weight-bold mb-0 text-info"><%= stats.countQR.toLocaleString() %> <small class="h6 text-muted">฿</small></h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="table-container mb-5 shadow-sm border">
            <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="table table-hover mb-0">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th class="pl-4">วันที่บันทึก</th>
                            <th>รายการสินค้า</th>
                            <th>ชื่อลูกค้า</th>
                            <th class="text-center">การชำระเงิน</th>
                            <th class="text-right">ส่วนลด</th>
                            <th class="text-right pr-4">ยอดสุทธิ</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <% if (sales.length > 0) { %>
                            <% sales.forEach(sale => { %>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="pl-4">
                                    <div class="text-dark font-weight-bold mb-0" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">
                                        <%= moment(sale.date).format('DD MMM YYYY') %>
                                    </div>
                                    <small class="text-muted"><%= moment(sale.date).format('HH:mm') %> น.</small>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <span class="product-name"><%= sale.product ? sale.product.name : 'ไม่มีข้อมูลสินค้า' %></span>
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="member-info">
                                        <i class="far fa-user-circle mr-1"></i> 
                                        <%= sale.member ? sale.member.name : 'ลูกค้าทั่วไป' %>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                                <td class="text-center">
                                    <% if(sale.paymentMethod === 'Cash') { %>
                                        <span class="badge-pay bg-light text-dark border"><i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave mr-1"></i> เงินสด</span>
                                    <% } else if(sale.paymentMethod === 'QR') { %>
                                        <span class="badge-pay" style="background: rgba(33, 147, 176, 0.1); color: #2193b0;"><i class="fas fa-qrcode mr-1"></i> QR Code</span>
                                    <% } else { %>
                                        <span class="badge-pay" style="background: rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.1); color: #28a745;"><i class="fas fa-university mr-1"></i> โอนเงิน</span>
                                    <% } %>
                                </td>
                                <td class="text-right">
                                    <span class="text-danger font-weight-bold" style="font-size: 0.85rem;">
                                        <%= sale.discount > 0 ? '-' + sale.discount.toLocaleString() : '0' %>
                                    </span>
                                </td>
                                <td class="text-right pr-4">
                                    <span class="h6 font-weight-bold text-dark"><%= sale.totalPrice.toLocaleString() %> ฿</span>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <% }) %>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <tr>
                                <td colspan="6" class="text-center py-5">
                                    <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/7486/7486744.png" width="80" class="mb-3 opacity-50">
                                    <h5 class="text-muted">ไม่พบประวัติการขายในระบบ</h5>
                                    <p class="text-muted small">ลองเปลี่ยนช่วงวันที่ที่ต้องการค้นหาอีกครั้ง</p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        <% } %>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>